{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji45.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给毛岸青的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给毛岸青\"的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1962年1月12日）岸青儿："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄来的信，收到，甚为高兴。你现在住院治疗，望遵医嘱，不要变方法治疗、休息。一切待今年上半年机会成熟时，就会解决的。我好，时有点小毛病，一下子就过去了，忽（勿）以为念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六二年一月十二日[1]毛岸青，毛泽东的儿子。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":1,"day":12}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":44,"page_end":44},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}